puts "Welcome to the all knowing, all seeing computer gussing game. Can you guess what number I am thinking of?"
x = rand(11)
sleep 10
puts "I'm thinking of a number between 0 and 10. Now try and think of what number that is."
sleep 5
puts "Do you have a number in mind?"
sleep 2
puts "OK lets hear it, type it in."
guess = gets.chomp.to_i

until guess == x
  puts "Nope you ignorant DOPE. Try again!"
  guess = gets.chomp.to_i
end

puts "That's right! I was thinking of #{x}"
